creator: Feeld Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Chat & connect on alternative dating platform Feeld. From open-minded couples to curious singles, Feeld is open to everyone looking to explore their dating desires in a safe and private space.

Dating for humans. Feeld is the alternative dating platform for couples and singles, open to all genders and sexual identities. A space where you can explore your desires and find your humans, Feeld is one of the largest open-minded communities worldwide.

Find your humans anywhere in the world

Connect with humans worldwide in Feeld’s new virtual cores.

Private

Be open, not exposed. Explore your desires in a safe & private space.

For Open-Minded Humans

We offer the option to pair profiles with a partner, a lover or a curious friend and to explore Feeld as a couple.

20+ sexual identities to choose from including:

Heterosexual. Bisexual. Heteroflexible. Homosexual. Pansexual. Queer.

20+ gender identities to choose from and search for including:

Agender. Cisgender. Gender Queer. Non-Binary. Transgender.

Become Majestic

Feeld is free to use but for the full Feeld experience, there is our Majestic membership. It comes with enhanced features such who has liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections and enjoying more extensive privacy options.

As seen in: VICE, New York Times, Dazed & Confused, The Times et al.

______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

All personal data is handled under the Terms and Conditions of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here:

https://feeld.co/privacy-policy
descriptionShort: Chat and connect with curious couples and singles.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Isolation doesn't mean the end of pleasure. You can now connect with self-isolating humans worldwide in Feeld’s new virtual cores.
- You’ll also find a range of improvements throughout the app, including the login and registration processes.

title: Feeld: Dating & Chat For Couples & Singles

creator: Feeld Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Chat & connect on alternative dating app Feeld. From open-minded couples to curious singles, Feeld is open to everyone looking to explore their dating desires in a safe and private online dating space.

Online dating for humans. Feeld is the alternative dating app for couples and singles, open to all - heterosexual, bisexual, gay, pansexual, queer, agender, non-binary, transgender. Feeld has over 20 sexual identities and gender identities to choose from. An online dating space where you can explore your desires and find your humans, Feeld is one of the largest open-minded dating communities worldwide.

Find your humans anywhere in the world

Connect with humans worldwide in Feeld’s new virtual cores.

Private

Be open, not exposed. Explore your dating desires in a safe & private online space.

For Open-Minded Humans

We offer the option to pair profiles with a partner, a lover or a curious friend and to explore Feeld as a couple. Find your humans in a safe, online dating environment. Whether you’re looking for couples dating, bisexual singles or for a throuple (threeway couple), Feeld is your open and inclusive online dating app. 

20+ sexual identities to choose from including:

Heterosexual. Bisexual. Heteroflexible. Homosexual. Pansexual. Queer.

20+ gender identities to choose from and search for including:

Agender. Cisgender. Gender Queer. Non-Binary. Transgender.

Become Majestic

Feeld is free to use but for the full Feeld experience, there is our Majestic membership. It comes with enhanced features such who has liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections and enjoying more extensive privacy options.

As seen in: VICE, New York Times, Dazed & Confused, The Times et al.

______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

All personal data is handled under the Terms and Conditions of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here:

title:
Feeld: Meet Couples & Singles
7.0.0

creator: Feeld Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Feeld: the dating app for the curious. Feeld was made for you to connect with open-minded singles and couples looking to explore dating and relationships in a safe and private way. Chat & connect on an alternative dating app created for everyone, no matter their relationship status. From open-minded couples to curious singles, Feeld is open to anyone looking for an exciting, new type of dating experience.

Discover a space to be your true self and let the people looking for you find you. Join Feeld solo, with a partner, or a curious friend to explore virtual or other locations and connect with like-minded individuals worldwide. Connect openly in a diverse community open to all genders and sexual identities as you redefine your relationships to self and others on Feeld.

Discover an open-minded dating experience when you download today.


FEELD FEATURES

CHAT & CONNECT
• Meet open-minded humans and start up a conversation
• Connect with people closest to you, or explore 20+ of our most popular cities around the world
• Find couples and singles looking to connect and discover a new way to date

A DATING APP MADE FOR EVERYONE
• Choose from over 20 gender identities
• Pick from a list of 20+ sexualities to personalize your Feeld experience
• Explore Feeld single or pair with a partner to find other open-minded people

DATE YOUR WAY
• Explore safely on a secure and private dating platform
• Connect with curious Feeld members and explore your desires
• Chat with couples and open-minded Feeld members for meaningful, intimate experiences

As seen in: New York Times, The New Yorker, Dazed & Confused, Cosmopolitan and Vanity Fair.

Become Majestic for the full Feeld experience. With a Majestic membership, you can enjoy enhanced features such as seeing who liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections, one free Ping a day, and more.

Download Feeld, a place to explore curiosity and desires, and date in a different way. Join solo or with a friend or couple and connect with other people around the world that are ready for a new, exciting way to date.

______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

The app is free to download and use.

Additional features are available when you join the Majestic Membership, an optional paid subscription service that funds the app’s development.

Subscriptions must be managed by the members and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the Play Store Subscriptions screen after purchase.

When a trial subscription is offered, the trial period begins when a member signs up for the subscription through their Play Store account. The subscription will be charged on the last day of the trial unless the member cancels at least 24 hours before trial ends.

Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the member purchases a subscription.

To cancel the Membership, members must cancel directly through their Play Store account.

Cancellations begin at the end of the current subscription period.

All purchases are billed to the payment method that you designate when you sign up for a Google Play account as part of your Play Store account and will appear as Google on your Play Store statement.

All personal data is handled under the Terms of Use of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/privacy.

Terms of Use can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/terms

title:
Feeld: Meet Couples & Singles
7.5.2

creator: Feeld Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Feeld was made for you to connect with open-minded people looking to explore dating and relationships in a safe and private way. Chat & connect on an alternative dating app created for anyone and everyone. Feeld is open to anyone looking for an exciting, new type of dating experience.

Discover a space to be your true self and let the people looking for you find you. Join Feeld to explore virtual or other locations and connect with like-minded individuals worldwide. Connect openly in a diverse community open to all genders and sexual identities as you redefine your relationships to self and others on Feeld.

Discover an open-minded dating experience when you download today.


FEELD FEATURES

CHAT & CONNECT
• Meet open-minded humans and start up a conversation
• Connect with people closest to you, or explore 20+ of our most popular cities around the world
• Find people looking to connect and discover a new way to date

A DATING APP MADE FOR EVERYONE
• Choose from over 20 gender identities
• Pick from a list of 20+ sexualities to personalize your Feeld experience

DATE YOUR WAY
• Explore safely on a secure and private dating platform
• Connect with curious Feeld members and explore your desires
• Chat with open-minded Feeld members for meaningful, intimate experiences

As seen in: New York Times, The New Yorker, Dazed & Confused, Cosmopolitan and Vanity Fair.

Become Majestic for the full Feeld experience. With a Majestic membership, you can enjoy enhanced features such as seeing who liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections, one free Ping a day, and more.

Download Feeld, a place to explore curiosity and desires, and date in a different way. Connect with other people around the world that are ready for a new, exciting way to date.


______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

The app is free to download and use.

Additional features are available when you join the Majestic Membership, an optional paid subscription service that funds the app’s development.

Subscriptions must be managed by the members and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the Play Store Subscriptions screen after purchase.

When a trial subscription is offered, the trial period begins when a member signs up for the subscription through their Play Store account. The subscription will be charged on the last day of the trial unless the member cancels at least 24 hours before trial ends.

Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the member purchases a subscription.

To cancel the Membership, members must cancel directly through their Play Store account.

Cancellations begin at the end of the current subscription period.

All purchases are billed to the payment method that you designate when you sign up for a Google Play account as part of your Play Store account and will appear as Google on your Play Store statement.

All personal data is handled under the Terms of Use of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/privacy.

Terms of Use can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/terms

Feeld was made for you to connect with open-minded people looking to explore dating and relationships in a safe and private way. Chat & connect on an alternative dating app created for anyone and everyone. Feeld is open to anyone looking for an exciting, new type of dating experience.

Discover a space to be your true self and let the people looking for you find you. Join Feeld to explore virtual or other locations and connect with like-minded individuals worldwide. Connect openly in a diverse community open to all genders and sexual identities as you redefine your relationships to self and others on Feeld.

Discover an open-minded dating experience when you download today.


FEELD FEATURES

CHAT & CONNECT
• Meet open-minded humans and start up a conversation
• Connect with people closest to you, or explore 20+ of our most popular cities around the world
• Find people looking to connect and discover a new way to date

A DATING APP MADE FOR EVERYONE
• Choose from over 20 gender identities
• Pick from a list of 20+ sexualities to personalize your Feeld experience

DATE YOUR WAY
• Explore safely on a secure and private dating platform
• Connect with curious Feeld members and explore your desires
• Chat with open-minded Feeld members for meaningful, intimate experiences

As seen in: New York Times, The New Yorker, Dazed & Confused, Cosmopolitan and Vanity Fair.

Become Majestic for the full Feeld experience. With a Majestic membership, you can enjoy enhanced features such as seeing who liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections, one free Ping a day, and more.

Download Feeld, a place to explore curiosity and desires, and date in a different way. Connect with other people around the world that are ready for a new, exciting way to date.


______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

The app is free to download and use.

Additional features are available when you join the Majestic Membership, an optional paid subscription service that funds the app’s development.

Subscriptions must be managed by the members and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the Play Store Subscriptions screen after purchase.

When a trial subscription is offered, the trial period begins when a member signs up for the subscription through their Play Store account. The subscription will be charged on the last day of the trial unless the member cancels at least 24 hours before trial ends.

Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the member purchases a subscription.

To cancel the Membership, members must cancel directly through their Play Store account.

Cancellations begin at the end of the current subscription period.

All purchases are billed to the payment method that you designate when you sign up for a Google Play account as part of your Play Store account and will appear as Google on your Play Store statement.

All personal data is handled under the Terms of Use of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/privacy.

Terms of Use can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/terms

Feeld: Meet Couples & Singles
7.20.0

creator: Feeld Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Feeld was made for you to connect with open-minded people looking to explore dating and relationships in a safe and private way. Chat & connect on an alternative dating app created for anyone and everyone. Feeld is open to anyone looking for an exciting, new type of dating experience.

Discover a space to be your true self and let the people looking for you find you. Join Feeld to explore virtual or other locations and connect with like-minded individuals worldwide. Connect openly in a diverse community open to all genders and sexual identities as you redefine your relationships to self and others on Feeld.

Discover an open-minded dating experience when you download today.


FEELD FEATURES

CHAT & CONNECT
• Meet open-minded humans and start up a conversation
• Connect with people closest to you, or explore 20+ of our most popular cities around the world
• Find people looking to connect and discover a new way to date

A DATING APP MADE FOR EVERYONE
• Choose from over 20 gender identities
• Pick from a list of 20+ sexualities to personalize your Feeld experience

DATE YOUR WAY
• Explore safely on a secure and private dating platform
• Connect with curious Feeld members and explore your desires
• Chat with open-minded Feeld members for meaningful, intimate experiences

As seen in: New York Times, The New Yorker, Dazed & Confused, Cosmopolitan and Vanity Fair.

Become Majestic for the full Feeld experience. With a Majestic membership, you can enjoy enhanced features such as seeing who liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections, one free Ping a day, and more.

Download Feeld, a place to explore curiosity and desires, and date in a different way. Connect with other people around the world that are ready for a new, exciting way to date.


______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

The app is free to download and use.

Additional features are available when you join the Majestic Membership, an optional paid subscription service that funds the app’s development.

Subscriptions must be managed by the members and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the Play Store Subscriptions screen after purchase.

When a trial subscription is offered, the trial period begins when a member signs up for the subscription through their Play Store account. The subscription will be charged on the last day of the trial unless the member cancels at least 24 hours before trial ends.

Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the member purchases a subscription.

To cancel the Membership, members must cancel directly through their Play Store account.

Cancellations begin at the end of the current subscription period.

All purchases are billed to the payment method that you designate when you sign up for a Google Play account as part of your Play Store account and will appear as Google on your Play Store statement.

All personal data is handled under the Terms of Use of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/privacy.

Terms of Use can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/terms

Feeld was made for you to connect with open-minded people looking to explore dating and relationships in a safe and private way. Chat & connect on an alternative dating app created for anyone and everyone. Feeld is open to anyone looking for an exciting, new type of dating experience.

Discover a space to be your true self and let the people looking for you find you. Join Feeld to explore virtual or other locations and connect with like-minded individuals worldwide. Connect openly in a diverse community open to all genders and sexual identities as you redefine your relationships to self and others on Feeld.

Discover an open-minded dating experience when you download today.


FEELD FEATURES

CHAT & CONNECT
• Meet open-minded humans and start up a conversation
• Connect with people closest to you, or explore 20+ of our most popular cities around the world
• Find people looking to connect and discover a new way to date

A DATING APP MADE FOR EVERYONE
• Choose from over 20 gender identities
• Pick from a list of 20+ sexualities to personalize your Feeld experience

DATE YOUR WAY
• Explore safely on a secure and private dating platform
• Connect with curious Feeld members and explore your desires
• Chat with open-minded Feeld members for meaningful, intimate experiences

As seen in: New York Times, The New Yorker, Dazed & Confused, Cosmopolitan and Vanity Fair.

Become Majestic for the full Feeld experience. With a Majestic membership, you can enjoy enhanced features such as seeing who liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections, one free Ping a day, and more.

Download Feeld, a place to explore curiosity and desires, and date in a different way. Connect with other people around the world that are ready for a new, exciting way to date.


______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

The app is free to download and use.

Additional features are available when you join the Majestic Membership, an optional paid subscription service that funds the app’s development.

Subscriptions must be managed by the members and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the Play Store Subscriptions screen after purchase.

When a trial subscription is offered, the trial period begins when a member signs up for the subscription through their Play Store account. The subscription will be charged on the last day of the trial unless the member cancels at least 24 hours before trial ends.

Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the member purchases a subscription.

To cancel the Membership, members must cancel directly through their Play Store account.

Cancellations begin at the end of the current subscription period.

All purchases are billed to the payment method that you designate when you sign up for a Google Play account as part of your Play Store account and will appear as Google on your Play Store statement.

All personal data is handled under the Terms of Use of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/privacy.

Terms of Use can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/terms
descriptionShort: Dating app for the curious. Connect with open-minded people.

Feeld was made for you to connect with open-minded people looking to explore dating and relationships in a safe and private way. Chat & connect on an alternative dating app created for anyone and everyone. Feeld is open to anyone looking for an exciting, new type of dating experience.

Discover a space to be your true self and let the people looking for you find you. Join Feeld to explore virtual or other locations and connect with like-minded individuals worldwide. Connect openly in a diverse community open to all genders and sexual identities as you redefine your relationships to self and others on Feeld.

Discover an open-minded dating experience when you download today.


FEELD FEATURES

CHAT & CONNECT
• Meet open-minded humans and start up a conversation
• Connect with people closest to you, or explore 20+ of our most popular cities around the world
• Find people looking to connect and discover a new way to date

A DATING APP MADE FOR EVERYONE
• Choose from over 20 gender identities
• Pick from a list of 20+ sexualities to personalize your Feeld experience

DATE YOUR WAY
• Explore safely on a secure and private dating platform
• Connect with curious Feeld members and explore your desires
• Chat with open-minded Feeld members for meaningful, intimate experiences

As seen in: New York Times, The New Yorker, Dazed & Confused, Cosmopolitan and Vanity Fair.

Become Majestic for the full Feeld experience. With a Majestic membership, you can enjoy enhanced features such as seeing who liked you on the app, adding private photos visible only to your Connections, one free Ping a day, and more.

Download Feeld, a place to explore curiosity and desires, and date in a different way. Connect with other people around the world that are ready for a new, exciting way to date.


______

You must be at least 18 years of age to access and use Feeld.

The app is free to download and use.

Additional features are available when you join the Majestic Membership, an optional paid subscription service that funds the app’s development.

Subscriptions must be managed by the members and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the Play Store Subscriptions screen after purchase.

When a trial subscription is offered, the trial period begins when a member signs up for the subscription through their Play Store account. The subscription will be charged on the last day of the trial unless the member cancels at least 24 hours before trial ends.

Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the member purchases a subscription.

To cancel the Membership, members must cancel directly through their Play Store account.

Cancellations begin at the end of the current subscription period.

All purchases are billed to the payment method that you designate when you sign up for a Google Play account as part of your Play Store account and will appear as Google on your Play Store statement.

All personal data is handled under the Terms of Use of Feeld Privacy Policy. More details can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/privacy.

Terms of Use can be found here: https://feeld.co/about/terms
descriptionShort: Date, Meet, Chat & Connect with Curious People

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: No big changes for Members in this release, but here’s something to keep in mind: Pings with Notes are 33% more likely to be accepted than those without. A little context goes a long way.
